title: 6th
description:
English:
Every desire exposes what us humans are capable of. In the end, it's just you and I, a chance for retribution, and some forgiveness in hindsight.

Spanish:
Cada deseo expone lo que los humanos somos capaces de hacer. Al final, somos solo tú y yo, una oportunidad de venganza y algo de perdón en retrospectiva.
